quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,By the fig and the olive
  95,2,"and [by] Mount Sinai"
  95,3,"and [by] this secure city [Mecca]"
  95,4,We have certainly created the human being in the best of stature
  95,5,Then We return him to the lowest of the low
  95,6,"except for those who believe and do righteous deeds, for they will have an uninterrupted reward"
  95,7,"So, do you still deny this faith"
  95,8,Isn't God the most Just of Judges